2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper involves motion magnification and time interpolation techniques for video processing. 
3. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper deals with recognizing human emotions through facial expressions. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper involves training a model to recognize subtle facial expressions. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves analyzing and extracting information from video data.
